2014-05-07, Version 1.1

* Change license from LGPL to MIT License
+ Add documents
+ Add method .open to Tian.App instances
+ Add method .open to Tian.Widget.MainPanel instances
+ Add namespace Tian.Temp for dynamic resources accessing
* Tian.i18n supports arbitrary dictionaries set by the second argument
* In Tian.Lang, the short language code will be used if the long one not available
+ Add animations of window when set to min or max state
- Remove dblclick event handler of window taskbar icon

